---
/** Franja “en taller” + sección flujo con SVG. */
---
      <div
        data-landing-reveal
        style="--lr-delay: 40ms"
        class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-200/70 dark:border-amber-800/60 bg-linear-to-r from-amber-50/90 via-white/80 to-sky-50/70 dark:from-amber-950/35 dark:via-gray-950/40 dark:to-sky-950/25 px-5 py-4 shadow-sm"
      >
        <p class="m-0 text-sm font-medium text-amber-950/95 dark:text-amber-100/90 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.devStrip">
          Parte del producto ya puedes usarlo con invitación; el resto está en el taller. Sin fechas mágicas ni humo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-10">
        <div class="h-px w-full bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-gray-200/80 to-transparent dark:via-gray-800/80" />
      </div>

      <section
        data-landing-reveal
        style="--lr-delay: 60ms"
        class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/55 dark:bg-gray-950/45 shadow-sm overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div class="px-6 py-5 border-b border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800/70 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 backdrop-blur flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-3">
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase" data-i18n="landing.flowKicker">Flujo</p>
            <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.flowTitle">Del proyecto al portfolio, con evidencias.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-xl" data-i18n="landing.flowSubtitle">
            Una relación visual: empieza pegando URLs, cuenta la historia y publica.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative p-6" data-landing-flow>
          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 260" class="w-full h-full" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="flowStroke" x1="0" x2="1" y1="0" y2="0">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgb(99 102 241)" stop-opacity="0.55" />
                  <stop offset="50%" stop-color="rgb(56 189 248)" stop-opacity="0.45" />
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgb(244 63 94)" stop-opacity="0.50" />
                </linearGradient>
                <filter id="flowBlur" x="-20%" y="-40%" width="140%" height="180%">
                  <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="8" />
                </filter>
              </defs>
              <path
                d="M 120 150 C 280 60, 420 60, 560 150 S 840 240, 1080 140"
                stroke="url(#flowStroke)"
                stroke-width="6"
                fill="none"
                filter="url(#flowBlur)"
              />
              <path
                id="landing-flow-path"
                d="M 120 150 C 280 60, 420 60, 560 150 S 840 240, 1080 140"
                stroke="url(#flowStroke)"
                stroke-width="2.25"
                fill="none"
                opacity="0.9"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="relative grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
            <div class="landing-flow-card rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/75 dark:bg-gray-950/65 p-6 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
                <div class="space-y-1">
                  <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.flowCard1Title">Evidencias</p>
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.flowCard1Body">
                    Pega URLs y detectamos el tipo para embed o enlace en segundos.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 dark:bg-indigo-400/10 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300 border border-indigo-500/15 dark:border-indigo-400/15">
                  🔗
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="landing-flow-card rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/75 dark:bg-gray-950/65 p-6 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
                <div class="space-y-1">
                  <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.flowCard2Title">Historia</p>
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.flowCard2Body">
                    Rol + resultado para que el proyecto se entienda sin contexto.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-sky-500/10 dark:bg-sky-400/10 text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 border border-sky-500/15 dark:border-sky-400/15">
                  ✍️
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="landing-flow-card rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/75 dark:bg-gray-950/65 p-6 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
                <div class="space-y-1">
                  <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="landing.flowCard3Title">Portfolio</p>
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="landing.flowCard3Body">
                    Publica tarjetas limpias y filtrables cuando tú decidas.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <span class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-rose-500/10 dark:bg-rose-400/10 text-rose-700 dark:text-rose-300 border border-rose-500/15 dark:border-rose-400/15">
                  ✨
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>